OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781975160
OL,3,CTories win first Scottish by-election
OL,4,Csince 1967 as SNP vote collapses
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Press Association
OL,7,Fafter the win, Lumsden said: "I'm
OL,8,Flooking forward to getting down to
OL,9,FWestminster and really banging the
OL,10,Fdrum for Aberdeen and the oil and gas
OL,11,Findustry.
OL,13,F"Labour have got to take note ` this
OL,14,Fis a seismic victory tonight and they
OL,15,Fhave got to change course on oil and
OL,16,Fgas, they've got to change course on
OL,17,Fenergy.
OL,19,F"We need to have new licences, we need
OL,20,Fto scrap the (energy profits levy), we
OL,21,Fneed to save those jobs."
OL,26,@oD@^OUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@YO]
