OL,3,CTories win first Scottish by-election
OL,4,Csince 1967 as SNP vote collapses
OL,6,FWith Lumsden's first Scottish by-
OL,7,Felection win since 1967 ` comes as the
OL,8,Fformer holder of the seat Stephen
OL,9,FFlynn voiced his disquiet about the
OL,10,Fparty's campaign.
OL,12,FPosting on X after the SNP conceded
OL,13,Fdefeat in the contest, Flynn said: "A
OL,14,Ftough night in Aberdeen that some will
OL,15,Fneed to reflect on, quite heavily."
OL,17,FHe added: "We lost Aberdeen South to
OL,18,Fthe Tories in 2017, and we won it back
OL,19,Ftwo years later.
OL,26,@uD@dOUwD@cO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
