PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781975160
OL,3,CTories win first Scottish by-election
OL,4,Csince 1967 as SNP vote collapses
OL,6,F"I've no doubt that we can do so
OL,7,Fagain. If we get things right."
OL,9,FA senior party source also hit out at
OL,10,Fthe SNP's stance on oil and gas ` a
OL,11,Fkey issue in a city which has been
OL,12,Fdubbed as the oil and gas capital of
OL,13,FEurope ` suggesting voters do not
OL,14,Funderstand the party's energy policy
OL,15,For view it as "weak".
OL,17,FAlso posting on X, First Minister John
OL,18,FSwinney said he was "very
OL,19,Fdisappointed" with the result.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]wD@OOUwD@TO]zD@UOU{D@MO]
