OL,3,CTories win first Scottish by-election
OL,4,Csince 1967 as SNP vote collapses
OL,6,F"Very disappointed with the result in
OL,7,FAberdeen South, @theSNP vote remains
OL,8,Fstrong but it is clear that tactical
OL,9,Fvoting has had a real impact on the
OL,10,Fresult," he said, congratulating
OL,11,FLumsden and praising the efforts of
OL,12,FSNP candidate Richard Thomson.
OL,14,FSpeaking to journalists after the
OL,15,Fresult, Thomson said the Tories had
OL,16,F"thrown the kitchen sink" at the
OL,17,Fcampaign.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]xD@AOUxD@YO]
