OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781975160
OL,3,CTories win first Scottish by-election
OL,4,Csince 1967 as SNP vote collapses
OL,6,F"We like not to be out-campaigned, but
OL,7,Fon this occasion, I think, just the
OL,8,Fsheer amount of resources that we were
OL,9,Fup against made it difficult to get
OL,10,Fthe result we'd hoped for," he said.
OL,12,FThe guilty plea of former SNP chief
OL,13,Fexecutive ` and Nicola Sturgeon's
OL,14,Festranged husband ` Peter Murrell did
OL,15,Fnot "make a bit of difference" to the
OL,16,Fparty's fortunes in Thursday's poll,
OL,17,Fhe added.
OL,19,F"If anybody raised it, it was usually
OL,20,Fan indication that they weren't voting
OL,21,FSNP anyway.
