OL,3,CTories win first Scottish by-election
OL,4,Csince 1967 as SNP vote collapses
OL,6,FBird ` a lawyer and SNP adviser ` won
OL,7,F9,802 votes in Thursday's contest,
OL,8,Fwith Reform's Bill Reid second with
OL,9,F4,841.
OL,11,FSpeaking to the Press Association, Ms
OL,12,FBird said: "It was obviously the
OL,13,FTories' night up in Aberdeen this
OL,14,Fevening, and obviously that's a
OL,15,Fdisappointing result for us.
OL,17,F"But the circumstances are very
OL,18,Fdifferent. I'm just delighted for what
OL,19,Fwe were able to achieve here in
OL,20,FArbroath and Broughty Ferry.
OL,26,@tD@LOUyD@AOU
